[[row]]
[[cell style="text-align: center; border: 1px solid gray; padding: 1px;"]]
||||~ [[size smaller]]Table.1: 物理的性質[[/size]] ||
||~ [[size smaller]]波長[[/size]] || [[size smaller]]1.9×10^^-3^^m[[/size]] ||
||~ [[size smaller]]振動数[[/size]] || [[size smaller]]160.2Ghz[[/size]] ||
||~ [[size smaller]]スペクトル[[/size]] || [[size smaller]]2.725Kの黒体放射に極めてよく一致[[/size]] ||
